service

Class StudyService

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.StudyService

  • @Component
public class StudyService
extends java.lang.Object
    StudyService class provides methods for dealing with Study objects, getting list of available topics, getting next Card object from some shuffled sequence and processing user's answers.
    Author:
    Aleksandr Gaslov

      • nextCard

        public Card nextCard()
        Returns next Card from previously prepared shuffled list. Cards with priority '3' appears 4 times per study. Cards with priority '2' appears 3 times per study. Cards with priority '1' appears 2 times per study.
        Returns:
        next Card according its priority or null if there is no next Card

      • processAnswer

        public boolean processAnswer(Card card,
                    java.lang.String answer)
        Returns if received answer matches Card translation. Increments counter of answered questions of the corresponding History object. If answer is correct, increments counter of correct answers of the corresponding History object. If correct answer is second in succession for given Card, Card's priority decrements. If answer is not correct, Card's priority increments.
        Parameters:
        card - - Card being answered
        answer - - user's answer
        Returns:
        true if answer is correct, false otherwise
